{"page_id": 53850, "slug": "Crossover_characters", "title": "Crossover characters", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Crossover characters</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "Characters from other series and franchises guest staring in Neon Genesis Evangelion in official crossovers from any media.\n\n==Godzilla vs Evangelion==\n===Godzilla===\n{{expand}}\n===King Ghidorah===\n{{expand}}\n\n==Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”==\n{{MontageBox\n|float   = left\n|columns = 1\n|title   = \n|colour  = \n|image1  = [[File:Transformers x Evangelion- Transformers mode “EVA” Chapter 3 cover.jpeg|300px]]\n|caption = Optimus Prime-Eva fighting Angel-scream\n}}\n===Optimus Prime===\nThe leader of the Autobots. He came to Earth aboard Sky Lynx. When he fought Angel-scream, he scanned Unit 01, gaining its massive size and an approximation of the powers and called himself Optimus Prime-Eva. After the defeat of Angel-scream, he and his fellow Autobots forged an alliance with Nerv to counter future threats.\n{{-}}\n{{MontageBox\n|float   = right\n|columns = 1\n|title   = \n|colour  = \n|image1  = [[File:Transformers x Evangelion- Transformers mode “EVA” Chapter 1 cover.jpeg|300px]] \n|caption =Angel-scream up top, Bottom row left to right: Wheeljack, Sideswipe, Optimus Prime, Bumblebee\n}}\n===Starscream/Angel-scream===\nAfter having died in the [https://tfwiki.net/wiki/Unicron_War Unicron War], his ghost went on to possoss an Angel on Earth. He was lured into a trap in a joint operation between Nerv and the Autobots, had his core ripped out and his spirit was banished into outer space.\n\n===Bumblebee===\nBumblebee was one of the Autobots on Sky Lynx. During the battle, he led Angel-scream into a trap set by Misato.\n\n===Sky Lynx===\nSky Lynx was the Autobot shuttle who brought the Autobots to Tokyo-3. Only appears in the first chapter.\n\n===Sideswipe===\nSideswipe was one of the Autobots arriving in Sky Lynx to Tokyo-3. Fights Angel-scream alongside Optimus Prime.\n\n===Wheeljack===\nWheeljack was one of the Autobots arriving in Sky Lynx to Tokyo-3. Misato contacted Wheeljack with information on Angels after it became apparent that they would need to help out in the fighting. After the battle, Wheeljack was seen talking to the NERV Scientists.\n{{-}}\n{{reflist}}\n{{expand}}\n{{cleanup}}\n[[Category:Evangelions]]\n[[Category:Angels]]\n[[Category:Evangelion Characters]]\n[[Category: Crossovers]]\n{{Evangelion List}}\n{{Character List}}\n{{Angel List}}", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>Characters from other series and franchises guest staring in Neon Genesis Evangelion in official crossovers from any media.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Godzilla_vs_Evangelion\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Godzilla vs Evangelion</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Godzilla\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Godzilla</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#King_Ghidorah\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">King Ghidorah</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Transformers_x_Evangelion:_Transformers_mode_“EVA”\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Optimus_Prime\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Optimus Prime</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Starscream/Angel-scream\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Starscream/Angel-scream</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Bumblebee\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bumblebee</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Sky_Lynx\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Sky Lynx</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Sideswipe\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Sideswipe</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Wheeljack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wheeljack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Godzilla_vs_Evangelion\">Godzilla vs Evangelion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Godzilla vs Evangelion\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Godzilla\">Godzilla</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Godzilla\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseagreen; width:85%; background:honeydew;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/180px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/270px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/360px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>Making something... Nurturing something is really great. You can see and learn so many things from the process.</i>\"</b></big><br />\nPlease help improve this article or section by <b>expanding it.</b><br />\n<small>If you have questions on what to improve/expand, please discuss on the talk page.</small>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"King_Ghidorah\">King Ghidorah</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: King Ghidorah\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseagreen; width:85%; background:honeydew;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/180px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/270px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/360px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>Making something... Nurturing something is really great. You can see and learn so many things from the process.</i>\"</b></big><br />\nPlease help improve this article or section by <b>expanding it.</b><br />\n<small>If you have questions on what to improve/expand, please discuss on the talk page.</small>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span id=\"Transformers_x_Evangelion:_Transformers_mode_.E2.80.9CEVA.E2.80.9D\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transformers_x_Evangelion:_Transformers_mode_“EVA”\">Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table style=\"float: left; clear: left; width: 1px; text-align: center; vertical-align: center; font-size: 90%; background-color: white; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; margin: 1em;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/9/90/Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg/300px-Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"212\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/90/Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg/450px-Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/90/Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg/600px-Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_3_cover.jpeg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left; valign: top;\">\n<p>Optimus Prime-Eva fighting Angel-scream\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Optimus_Prime\">Optimus Prime</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Optimus Prime\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The leader of the Autobots. He came to Earth aboard Sky Lynx. When he fought Angel-scream, he scanned Unit 01, gaining its massive size and an approximation of the powers and called himself Optimus Prime-Eva. After the defeat of Angel-scream, he and his fellow Autobots forged an alliance with Nerv to counter future threats.\n<br clear=\"all\" />\n</p>\n<table style=\"float: right; clear: right; width: 1px; text-align: center; vertical-align: center; font-size: 90%; background-color: white; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; margin: 1em;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg/300px-Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"212\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg/450px-Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg/600px-Transformers_x_Evangelion-_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D_Chapter_1_cover.jpeg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left; valign: top;\">\n<p>Angel-scream up top, Bottom row left to right: Wheeljack, Sideswipe, Optimus Prime, Bumblebee\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h3><span id=\"Starscream.2FAngel-scream\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Starscream/Angel-scream\">Starscream/Angel-scream</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Starscream/Angel-scream\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After having died in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://tfwiki.net/wiki/Unicron_War\">Unicron War</a>, his ghost went on to possoss an Angel on Earth. He was lured into a trap in a joint operation between Nerv and the Autobots, had his core ripped out and his spirit was banished into outer space.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bumblebee\">Bumblebee</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Bumblebee\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Bumblebee was one of the Autobots on Sky Lynx. During the battle, he led Angel-scream into a trap set by Misato.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sky_Lynx\">Sky Lynx</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Sky Lynx\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Sky Lynx was the Autobot shuttle who brought the Autobots to Tokyo-3. Only appears in the first chapter.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sideswipe\">Sideswipe</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Sideswipe\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Sideswipe was one of the Autobots arriving in Sky Lynx to Tokyo-3. Fights Angel-scream alongside Optimus Prime.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wheeljack\">Wheeljack</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Crossover_characters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Wheeljack\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wheeljack was one of the Autobots arriving in Sky Lynx to Tokyo-3. Misato contacted Wheeljack with information on Angels after it became apparent that they would need to help out in the fighting. After the battle, Wheeljack was seen talking to the NERV Scientists.\n<br clear=\"all\" />\n</p>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n</div>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseagreen; width:85%; background:honeydew;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/180px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/270px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/360px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>Making something... Nurturing something is really great. You can see and learn so many things from the process.</i>\"</b></big><br />\nPlease help improve this article or section by <b>expanding it.</b><br />\n<small>If you have questions on what to improve/expand, please discuss on the talk page.</small>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid darkslategray; width:85%; background:gainsboro;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/9/9a/19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg/135px-19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"135\" height=\"103\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9a/19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg/203px-19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9a/19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg/270px-19_C029_eva03-mess.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><big><b>\"<i>When Aoba called B Wing's construction sloppy he hadn't seen anything like THIS!</i>\"</b></big><br />\n<p>This article or section may require a <b>cleanup</b> to meet a standard of quality that isn't plain embarrassing.<br />\n<small>Please discuss this issue on the talk page and/or begin editing the page.</small><br />\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox centered\" style=\"width: 60%; font-size: 90%; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; clear: both\" align=\"center\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background: DarkSeaGreen; font-size: 110%;\"><i><b><a href=\"/Evangelions_(Portal)\" title=\"Evangelions (Portal)\">Evangelions</a></b></i>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/Evangelions\" title=\"Evangelions\">Evangelions</a> (general)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/Failed_Evangelion_Prototypes\" title=\"Failed Evangelion Prototypes\">Failed Evangelion Prototypes</a> | <a href=\"/Simulation_Bodies\" title=\"Simulation Bodies\">Simulation Bodies</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-00\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-00\">Eva-00</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-01\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-01\">Eva-01</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-02\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-02\">Eva-02</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-03\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-03\">Eva-03</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-04\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-04\">Eva-04</a> | <a href=\"/Mass_Production_Evangelions\" title=\"Mass Production Evangelions\">Mass Production Evangelions</a> (Evas 05~13)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b><a href=\"/Rebuild_of_Evangelion\" title=\"Rebuild of Evangelion\">Rebuild of Evangelion</a></b>: <a href=\"/Evangelion_Mark.04\" title=\"Evangelion Mark.04\">Mark.04</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-05\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-05\">Eva-05</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Mark.06\" title=\"Evangelion Mark.06\">Mark.06</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-08\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-08\">Eva-08</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Mark.09\" title=\"Evangelion Mark.09\">Mark.09</a> | <a href=\"/Evangelion_13\" title=\"Evangelion 13\">Eva-13</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit_8_Plus_2\" title=\"Evangelion Unit 8 Plus 2\">Eva 8+2</a>