mplate:Cleanup\n  6.69%    1.170      2 Template:Br\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key mediawikidb-ew_:pcache:idhash:53850-0!canonical and timestamp 20260416205831 and revision id 107312. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>", "summary": "Characters from other series and franchises guest staring in Neon Genesis Evangelion in official crossovers from any media.", "sections": [{"toclevel": 1, "level": "2", "line": "Godzilla vs Evangelion", "number": "1", "index": "1", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 125, "anchor": "Godzilla_vs_Evangelion", "linkAnchor": "Godzilla_vs_Evangelion"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Godzilla", "number": "1.1", "index": "2", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 152, "anchor": "Godzilla", "linkAnchor": "Godzilla"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "King Ghidorah", "number": "1.2", "index": "3", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 178, "anchor": "King_Ghidorah", "linkAnchor": "King_Ghidorah"}, {"toclevel": 1, "level": "2", "line": "Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”", "number": "2", "index": "4", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 210, "anchor": "Transformers_x_Evangelion:_Transformers_mode_“EVA”", "linkAnchor": "Transformers_x_Evangelion:_Transformers_mode_“EVA”"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Optimus Prime", "number": "2.1", "index": "5", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 483, "anchor": "Optimus_Prime", "linkAnchor": "Optimus_Prime"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Starscream/Angel-scream", "number": "2.2", "index": "6", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 1108, "anchor": "Starscream/Angel-scream", "linkAnchor": "Starscream/Angel-scream"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Bumblebee", "number": "2.3", "index": "7", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 1410, "anchor": "Bumblebee", "linkAnchor": "Bumblebee"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Sky Lynx", "number": "2.4", "index": "8", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 1540, "anchor": "Sky_Lynx", "linkAnchor": "Sky_Lynx"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Sideswipe", "number": "2.5", "index": "9", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 1661, "anchor": "Sideswipe", "linkAnchor": "Sideswipe"}, {"toclevel": 2, "level": "3", "line": "Wheeljack", "number": "2.6", "index": "10", "fromtitle": "Crossover_characters", "byteoffset": 1790, "anchor": "Wheeljack", "linkAnchor": "Wheeljack"}], "categories": ["Evangelions", "Angels", "Evangelion Characters", " Crossovers"], "infobox": {}, "templates": ["expand", "Evangelion List", "MontageBox", "Angel List", "cleanup", "-", "reflist", "Character List"], "internal_links": [], "external_links": ["https://tfwiki.net/wiki/Unicron_War"], "iw_links": [], "lang_links": [], "properties": [], "protection": [], "rev_id": 107312, "length_bytes": null, "parse_warnings": [], "touched_at": null, "references": [], "chunks": [{"article_slug": "Crossover_characters", "section": "", "content": "Characters from other series and franchises guest staring in Neon Genesis Evangelion in official crossovers from any media.\n\nGodzilla vs Evangelion\nGodzilla\n\nKing Ghidorah\n\nTransformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”\n\nOptimus Prime\nThe leader of the Autobots. He came to Earth aboard Sky Lynx. When he fought Angel-scream, he scanned Unit 01, gaining its massive size and an approximation of the powers and called himself Optimus Prime-Eva. After the defeat of Angel-scream, he and his fellow Autobots forged an alliance with Nerv to counter future threats.\n\nStarscream/Angel-scream\nAfter having died in the Unicron War, his ghost went on to possoss an Angel on Earth. He was lured into a trap in a joint operation between Nerv and the Autobots, had his core ripped out and his spirit was banished into outer space.\n\nBumblebee\nBumblebee was one of the Autobots on Sky Lynx. During the battle, he led Angel-scream into a trap set by Misato.\n\nSky Lynx\nSky Lynx was the Autobot shuttle who brought the Autobots to Tokyo-3. Only appears in the first chapter.\n\nSideswipe\nSideswipe was one of the Autobots arriving in Sky Lynx to Tokyo-3. Fights Angel-scream alongside Optimus Prime.\n\nWheeljack\nWheeljack was one of the Autobots arriving in Sky Lynx to Tokyo-3. Misato contacted Wheeljack with information on Angels after it became apparent that they would need to help out in the fighting. After the battle, Wheeljack was seen talking to the NERV Scientists.\n\nCategory:Evangelions\nCategory:Angels\nCategory:Evangelion Characters\nCategory: Crossovers", "position": 0, "token_count": 376}]}